<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="span12">
      <h1 style="text-align: center;">
        What Analysts Say About OutSystems
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="span8 top10">
      <p style=" margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Industry analysts across many coverage areas at firms such as <strong>Gartner</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>Forrester</strong>, <strong>IDC</strong>, <strong>451</strong>, <strong>OVUM</strong> and <strong>Bloor</strong> routinely cover OutSystems Platform.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: -10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Our rapid application delivery platform spans many computer industry coverage areas including:
      </p>
      <ul style="margin-left:30px; margin-bottom:10px;">
        <li style="margin-top: -10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
          <p>
            Rapid application development (RAD) platforms
          </p>
